dataset.name: ICE Rotterdam Coal, March 2018 (ATWH2018)
dataset.description:
Contract Size:1,000 metric tons

Deliverable Good:Contracts are financially settled based upon the price of coal delivered into the Amsterdam, Rotterdam, and Antwerp region in the Netherlands. The contract is cash settled against the API 2 Index published in the Argus/McCloskey Coal Price Index Report.

Tick Size:US dollars and cents per tonne

Pricing Unit:5 cents per tonne

Columns: Open, High, Low, Settle, Volume, Previous Day Open Interest. Note that Open Interest is always reported for the previous trading day, to avoid lookahead bias.
